<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="351" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="17.[151,1437,690,1255]" pageId="17" pageNumber="351">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1194,1219]" pageId="17" pageNumber="351">Remarks.</emphasis>
This new species resembles 
<taxonomicName authority="Viraktamath &amp; Mohan" authorityName="Viraktamath &amp; Mohan" box="[644,1013,1194,1219]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Scaphoideus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="351" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bifidus">
<emphasis box="[644,750,1195,1219]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="351">S. bifidus</emphasis>
Viraktamath &amp; Mohan
</taxonomicName>
in external shape and male genitalia, but differs in the shape of the connective processes.
</paragraph>
